This directory contains a script that can be used to generate all sub-mullers of a chosen focal barcoded lineage. Resulting submullers are stored in the local 'figures' sub-directory.

usage: plot_lineage_submullers.py [-h] [--fitness] [--color]
                                  [-highlight HIGHLIGHT] [-stopat STOPAT]
                                  pop_name parental_barcode

positional arguments:
  pop_name              name of population
  parental_barcode      parental barcode

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --fitness
  --color
  -highlight HIGHLIGHT  lineage to highlight
  -stopat STOPAT        number of barcodes after focal to plot